   "content": [
      {
         "id": "2923834e-bf4b-4d92-adad-c581b00ccf3d",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">En esta fase, tu objetivo es encontrar una respuesta y comprender las etapas del m\u00e9todo cient\u00edfico (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">En ciencias, cuando tenemos una idea, debemos ponerla a prueba para verificar si realmente explica algo. La ciencia no consiste en aceptar sin cuestionar, ni en creer ciegamente y desestimar lo contrario. La ciencia es un proceso continuo de aprendizaje diario.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Presentaci\u00f3n</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Nuestro objetivo es verificar si las figuras que se muestran a continuaci\u00f3n, que tienen las mismas longitudes y alturas, son iguales.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><table class=\"tawapukllay\" style=\"width: 50%;\"><tr><th>Cuadrado</th><th>C\u00edrculo</th></tr> <tr><td><div class=\"square\" style=\"background-color:lightblue;width:5.5vw;height:5.5vw\"></div></td> <td><i class=\"fa-solid fa-circle\" style=\"color:#FFCCCB;font-size:6vw;\"></i></td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "prev": "2923834e-bf4b-4d92-adad-c581b00ccf3d",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Nuestro primer paso es formular la pregunta que deseamos responder:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Sobre la igualdad</b><br />\u00bfSon iguales un cuadrado y un c\u00edrculo?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "prev": "66cf7457-cc81-4c29-8c20-48a4136a9bcb",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Ahora, definimos las hip\u00f3tesis (posibles respuestas) que vamos a poner a prueba:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIP\u00d3TESIS 1</b>: Son iguales.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIP\u00d3TESIS 2</b>: Son diferentes.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Realicemos algunos experimentos para obtener una <b>teor\u00eda</b> (la respuesta que buscamos) (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "prev": "55aed802-158f-4144-9b45-ad44aa674368",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": null,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Comparando partes</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Coloquemos una parte del c\u00edrculo sobre una parte del cuadrado:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"desc\"><div class=\"square\" style=\"width:3vw;height:3vw;background-color:lightblue;\"><div class=\"quartercircle\" style=\"width:3vw;height:3vw;background-color:#FFCCCB;\"></div></div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Las partes</b><br />\u00bfLa parte del c\u00edrculo cubre completamente la parte del cuadrado?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Al colocar solo una parte del c\u00edrculo sobre el cuadrado, es posible ver parte del cuadrado."
         ],
         "next": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "prev": "dc635f7b-cc08-498f-81a6-5ff52266ac62",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 2,
         "position": "topCenter"
      },
      {
         "id": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Comparando las figuras</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Tenemos indicios de que las figuras son diferentes. Para confirmarlo, coloquemos las figuras completas una sobre la otra:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"desc\"><div class=\"square\" style=\"width:6vw;height:6vw;background-color:lightblue;\"><div class=\"circle\" style=\"width:6vw;height:6vw;background-color:#FFCCCB;\"></div></div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>El todo</b><br />\u00bfEl c\u00edrculo cubre completamente el cuadrado?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Al colocar las figuras completas, nuevamente es posible ver parte del cuadrado detr\u00e1s."
         ],
         "next": "a3951d7c-99ed-45bc-9f73-ad0e601fd179",
         "prev": "062a5626-0e1f-4cc4-88b6-7b4128503dfd",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 0,
         "score": 2,
         "position": "top"
      },
      {
         "id": "a3951d7c-99ed-45bc-9f73-ad0e601fd179",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">Tabulaci\u00f3n</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Despu\u00e9s de los experimentos, podemos organizar los resultados en una tabla para compararlos:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><table class=\"indigenous_period\"><tr><th>Experimentos</th><th>Figuras iguales</th><th>Figuras diferentes</th></tr> <tr><th>Partes de las figuras</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td><b>X</b></td></tr> <tr><th>Figuras completas</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td><b>X</b></td></tr> </table>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection smGameTextSize\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Sobre los resultados</b><br />\u00bfPodemos decir que las figuras son diferentes?</div></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": [
            "Comparando los resultados, podemos afirmar que las figuras son diferentes."
         ],
         "next": "2ad76f9a-1d5c-4b2c-9a34-3b9edfdf3fed",
         "prev": "9521d6ae-79f8-4cdd-95e4-05bc56a6a301",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 2,
         "position": "topCenter"
      },
      {
         "id": "2ad76f9a-1d5c-4b2c-9a34-3b9edfdf3fed",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">La teor\u00eda (1/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Al inicio, ten\u00edamos dos hip\u00f3tesis:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIP\u00d3TESIS 1</b>: Son iguales.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><b>HIP\u00d3TESIS 2</b>: Son diferentes.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "a3c919d2-5e7e-4895-a830-81958c7ea473",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      },
      {
         "id": "a3c919d2-5e7e-4895-a830-81958c7ea473",
         "audio": "",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<span class=\"smGameTextTitleSize\">La teor\u00eda (2/2)</span><p class=\"smGameTextSize\">Despu\u00e9s de realizar los experimentos, podemos descartar la <b>HIP\u00d3TESIS 1</b> y formular una <b>teor\u00eda</b> (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('44acb900-ee84-4e42-8d9b-a947351af2cd'); return false;\">History Tracers (<span class=\"htdate\"></span>): Scientific Method</a>): un cuadrado es diferente de un c\u00edrculo.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"smGameTextSize\"><center><i class=\"fa-solid fa-medal\" style=\"color:gold; font-size: 5vw\"></i></center></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ],
         "desc": null,
         "next": "",
         "prev": "",
         "jumpTo": "",
         "answer": 1,
         "score": 1,
         "position": "center"
      }
   ],
